CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 26, 1952, pg. 27 reads: "Rugged Individual - Ted Benson, who'll be a line candidate for the Pittsburgh Steelers football team, appears as though he can handle himself. The six foot five inch former Morris Brown tackle weights 245 pounds. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Steelers Football team candidate Ted Benson posed in running stance, in Pitt Stadium, Oakland
